commentTextItems.html: played on the onside, batsmen do not want to run for a run but for their lives as the crowd quickly invades the pitch to work out some nice collectibles

commentPostTextItems.html: The chap who caught Kambli's six gets a booty of S$ 250 amongst the spectators Ganguly, the loser... sorry the losing captain on Lara the winning captain looks generally pleased, says the batting/bowling/fielding and everything else is very good with his game gets US$ 250 for getting the fastest fifty also wins the US$ 2,000 for the man of the match Lara says they won't be complacent for the finals as Tendulkar, Jadeja and Kumble will be playing in that match that is it folks, we will be thrilled to bring you yet another rain-reduced, closely-fought, multiple-sixes tri-nations final on Tuesday until then, good bye
